description: An officer in the sequel, Shin Koihime Musou. Despite her small size she`s a skillful warrior, wielding a sword that`s as long as she is tall. She`s quite fond of cats. She develops a huge crush on Kazuto, to the point of blushing profusely when the other members of the Wu faction tease her about it.
name: Shuutai Youhei
